TextBody:
Hello Phil,

Thank you for getting back and apologize for my late response.

If the one we worked yesterday was the correct disk, from the initial EPP virtual machine, then you should use it as a singular disk and boot from it.

Most likely the snapshot from February contains the boot issue, so we do not recommend to use it.

Looking forward for your response.

Best regards,
__________________

Hello Phil,

Thank you for getting back to us.
